 *
 * The MCP route (`src/servers/freddie-ai/routes/penny.ts`) imports:
 *   { daily, meeting, completeTask, setStatus, getDaily, search, moveTask, weekly, monthly, yearly, edit }
 *
 * This barrel re-exports all handlers so that import path resolution
 * from `../../../tools/penny.js` → `../../../tools/penny/index.js` (via the penny.ts shim)
 * continues to work without changes to the MCP route.
 */

